description: Redevelopment of site for residential purposes involving conversion of existing 5-storey office block into 30 flats (comprising 5 x studio, 25 x 1-bed) and erection of seven 3 and 4-storey blocks of 127 two-bed flats (25% of development for affordable housing) together with associated refuse store, cycle store, car parking, improvements to the junction of Melling Drive and Carterhatch Lane.
